- **Colors**: #404747 (neutral), #044441 (accent), #69D419 (accent), #2D6360 (accent), #FFFFFF (bg-light), #F4F8EA (bg-light), #FDFEFB (bg-light), #9AE761 (surface-light), #032E2C (accent), #2DD4BF (accent)
- **Fonts**: Inter (400,500,600,700,800), JetBrains Mono (400,500,600,700,800), Plus Jakarta Sans (700,800), Arial (400)
